                    </h4>
                    <p style={{ margin: '5px 0' }}>
                        üå°Ô∏è Í∏∞Ïò®: <strong>{forecast.TMP || '-'}¬∞C</strong> |
                        ‚òÅÔ∏è ÌïòÎäò ÏÉÅÌÉú: {getSkyDescription(forecast.SKY)}
                    </p>
                    <p style={{ margin: '5px 0' }}>
